1. User Registration and Login
As a user I want to create a account to access the game.
As a user I want to login without entering my credentials everytime.

2. Current Balance
As a user in my initial login I want to recieve initial virtual amount to start the trading.
As a user I want to view my current balance to track my performance.
________________________________________
3. Buying and Selling Assets
As a user, I want to buy assets so that I can invest my virtual money.
As a user, I want to sell assets so that I can make profit or reduce my losses.
________________________________________
4. Portfolio Tracking
As a user, I want to view my portfolio so that I can see what assets I own and their value.
As a user, I want to track my profit or loss so that I understand how well I am performing.
________________________________________
5. Leaderboard
As a user, I want to see a leaderboard so that I can compare my performance with other users.
As a user, I want to improve my ranking by making better trading decisions.
________________________________________

